{
  "stem": "58.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I joined, and we were meeting every month.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were talking about what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were stored-- we stored gasoline for Molotov cocktails, to make.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they knew where I-- where my-- where I live, so they getted some people from the same area, about 16 of us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said that this is you area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If the uprising comes to be, if they're going to ship us out, the first thing you have to do is burn-- there was a factory that made parts for airplanes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is your first duty, is to break the windows throw enough Molotov cocktails, this will go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, one day, first night of [DRINKS] first Passover-- excuse me, even I get my throat dry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first Passover night, first Seder, the ghetto is surrounded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Ukraines, there were-- they were the SS, also-- SS surrounded, like every 10 feet, an SS with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew this is it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- they called out, with loudspeakers, we should get in the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, nobody went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next day, they marched in, and we opened fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The guard was right about 10 feet from our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sitting on the roof.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They thought they marched in like usual, like nothing happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We opened fire.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we opened fire, a few fell, and they backed up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The backed out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They backed out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the meantime, a few of us had the order to burn this factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went to burn the factory, the factory went up in flames.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had to regroup, and we regrouped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got the orders, if tanks come in, we should throw some Molotov cocktails.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
